messages.message: Hey, does anyone own the NLP Search App? Had a customer asking about it, there doesn’t seem to be a ‘Search’ button, so you can’t actually run anything

it used to be owned by Aaron Vontell, so it’s technically owned by <#CER413NAE|>

It’s not actively being worked on, so I don’t think we should recommend customers to start using it

cc @lydia since we discussed deprecating NLP Search previously
Agreed! I am working with Nakul to formally deprecate it. It’s not being maintained at the moment
